"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.13\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.13</span> 标题：鳞甲、锁子铠甲（scale armor, coat of mail）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שִׁרְיוֹן, קַשְׂקֶשֶׂת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shiryon, shiryon qasqasim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5\">1SA 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5\">1SA 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38\">1SA 17:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:10\">NEH 4:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἁλυσιδωτός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：halusidōtos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:35\">1MA 6:35</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0389_scale_armor_detail.jpg\" alt=\"由金属圆片相互连接而成的鳞片盔甲特写\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">由金属圆片相互连接而成的鳞片盔甲特写 (© MatthiasKabel, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>鳞甲是一种背心或衬衣状的防护盔甲，遮盖住上半身。这种甲是用几百块鳞状或板状青铜片相互重叠，然后缝在布或皮革衬底上制成的。鳞片很薄，大小约11×6厘米（4.5×2.5英寸）。这种盔甲比实心金属胸甲要轻（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.12 护胸甲 (breastplate, chest protector)&lt;REALIA:2.12&gt;</a> ），还有较大的弹性，从而穿戴的人动作更加灵活。对于在战斗中不能携带盾牌但需要得到保护的士兵（例如战车的驭手），这种鳞甲尤其适合。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>很多语言都没有这种盔甲的专用名词。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5\">1SA 17:5</a> ，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 都采用了“coat of mail”（“锁子铠甲”）这个有些老旧的名称。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 译为“scale armor”（“鳞片盔甲”），而<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 译作“coat of……armor”（“……盔甲上衣”）。在不知道护身盔甲的文化中，翻译者可以说它是“一件盖满薄金属片、用来保护胸部的上衣”。</p>\n<p>亚哈王被敌人一支随意射出的箭射中了他所穿盔甲的某个薄弱处，因此阵亡（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:34\">1KI 22:34</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:33\">2CH 18:33</a> ）。表示这个盔甲上的薄弱处的希伯来文词语是<em>deveq</em> ，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 译为“scale armor”（“鳞片盔甲”），但这个词更有可能是指“盔甲两个部分之间的接缝”。翻译者也可以将这个词译为“他盔甲上的接缝”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译），或“他盔甲两个部分的接合处”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
